{
  "stem": "10587.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So every day, you got up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You did the same thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You lined up on the [INAUDIBLE], where you-- and they count.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Every day, they count you so that they know how many people left, and how many piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It got to the point where the kapos would, would take-- make us carry out dead bodies, and prop them up, and hold on to them so they can get more pieces of bread, the kapos.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because they counted the people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, and it was cold.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was-- actually, it, it seems like it was cold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because it must've been like maybe [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] August, I would say, roughly, and maybe because the-- you were always hungry.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That didn't help, either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So then they would call, and who wants seconds?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So when I saw that the people were pushing, you know, and they would-- and the kapos that would dish out the food would take the ladle and split your head with it, and the blood on the ladle.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And then they dunked it in again and, and poured the next.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So I realized right away that if I do that, I'll be killed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know, I'm not going to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And my father said, you know, same thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this went on for a few weeks like that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "What about the smells?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Did you--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The, the smell was horrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and the, the conditions were appall-- appalling conditions.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You-- because you, you, you didn't change your clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You couldn't, you couldn't take a shower.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't wash.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You, you [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] lived like an animal.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
